147
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,020
Come on.

148
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:29,020
Hello. Do you remember me?

149
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:32,020
Of course, Heidi. How could I forget you?

150
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:34,844
