151
00:12:34,844 --> 00:12:37,044
We just wanted to see how Schnucki is doing.

152
00:12:37,044 --> 00:12:40,644
Did you see that? She is healthy and cheerful and gives good milk.

153
00:12:40,644 --> 00:12:42,244
I can only thank you for that.

154
00:12:42,244 --> 00:12:43,644
Will you keep her?

155
00:12:43,644 --> 00:12:45,244
Don't ask such stupid questions.

156
00:12:46,644 --> 00:12:48,844
Goodbye. I have to go now.

157
00:12:50,644 --> 00:12:52,444
Please take good care of her.

158
00:12:52,444 --> 00:12:55,044
But of course. Now don't worry. I'll take care of her.

159
00:12:55,044 --> 00:12:56,044
As always.

160
